# run

## run macros
- run_online.C  : short online analysis during the experiment
- run_monitor.C : online analysis mornitor during the experiment
- run_conv.C : conversion from mfm to root
- run_reco.C : hit reconstruction
- run_viewer.C : GET channel viewer
- run_merger.C : LTEMerger
- run_ana_eve.C : create tree to run draw_and_fit_cross_section.C

## common configuration
- config_paths.mac : paths
- config_stark.mac : stark configuration
- config_type.mac  : run types

## outdated
- run_eve.C
- run_short.C

---

# drawing macros

## drawing macros and necessary files
- draw_and_fit_cross_section.C : create kinematics plot -> create energy plot for each theta -> create differential cross section.
    - set_draw_and_fit_cross_section.h
    - find_scaling_factor.C
    - functions.h
    - FitParInfo.h
    - data_x/et_kinematic_line.e[energy_index].[level_index].root
    - data_x/qt_edge.6789.root
    - data_lilak/anaX_e[energy_index]_cutX_ProtonCut.root
    - data_ana/KO2421_e[energy_index]_cutX_ProtonCut_NT360.ana_xmulth.root
    - data_x/theta_conversion.root
    - data_x/ggar_e[energy_index].root
    - data_x/argon_scattering_data.txt
    - data_x/fit_parameters_KO2421_e8_cutX_ProtonCut.ring12.linear_bg.dat
    - data_x/fit_parameters_KO2421_e8_cutX_ProtonCut.ring16.exp_bg.dat
- draw_blank_run_background.C : E/Q-value plot for background runs
    - data_ana/KO2421_blank_cutX_pidAll_NT360.ana_eve.root
    - data_x/example_e8_16.root
    - data_x/example_cut.root
- draw_detectors.C : draw stark silicon detector position in phi theta and their ids
    - reco files
- draw_event_count.C : draw event counts and merged kinematics plot for all runs
    - reco files
- draw_geometry_target_detector.C : draw geometrical position of experimental setup and create position error data file
- draw_junction_vs_ohmic.C : draw junction energy vs ohmic energy for all detectors
    - reco files
- draw_ko2421.C : draw plots for paper
    - data_x/x[energy_index].short.root
    - data_x/histQT_813_pair14_3.root
    - data_x/EVSTheta.root
- draw_phi_distribution.C : draw phi distribution of counts
    - reco files
- draw_psa.C : example PSA
    - reco files
- draw_summary.C : draw summary of draw_and_fit_cross_section.C
    - file from draw_and_fit_cross_section.C

## outdated
- draw_projection_histq.C
- draw_reco.C
- draw_relative_z.C
- draw_theta.C
- draw_theta_z.C
